{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21027.jpg","bgm":"bgm01_anime03","nameNarration":"Chisato","narration":"Everyone presented their ideas@for our original picture book, but@they were all a bit too out there.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"I, on the other hand, could only@think of a really typical, boring story."},{"narration":"I was really worried about what to do."},{"narration":"But then, I thought of an idea!"},{"narration":"And so, I got everyone together again.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_21027.jpg"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":1,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Chisato","nameRight":"Arisa","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"Well, what is it?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Haruka","textRight":"What's your idea, Chisato?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403201,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Matsuri","textRight":"Tell us, tell us!"},{"chara":[{"id":403401}],"textLeft":"Okay."},{"chara":[{"id":403401,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"But first, I want to thank everyone properly."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403401}],"textLeft":"Thank you so much for helping me."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Arisa","textRight":"Um..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Haruka","textRight":"You don't have to be so formal."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":403201,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Matsuri","textRight":"That's right! That's what friends are for!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"I just wanted to say it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":403401,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"Now, let me explain my idea."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Arisa","textRight":"Oooh, here it comes!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403401}],"textLeft":"I think it'll be difficult to use any of the@stories we came up with."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403201,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Matsuri","textRight":"Ohhh."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Haruka","textRight":"I agree. We should start over."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"Not exactly!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403401}],"textLeft":"I thought, what if we combine all of our@ideas into one?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Arisa","textRight":"All of them?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403501,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Haruka","textRight":"Make them one story?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":403201,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Matsuri","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":403201}],"textRight":"What do you mean?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":403401,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"The end of our last meeting was sort of@crazy."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":403401}],"textLeft":"But there was something that stuck with me."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":403401}],"textLeft":"So I decided to take parts from each of@our ideas..."},{"chara":[{"id":403401}],"textLeft":"...and turn them into one complete story."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":403401,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"This is what I came up with!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}